TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(ITEM.ITEM_ID) AS ITEM_ID, TRIM(ITEM.SAP_GRID_VALUE) AS SAP_GRID_VALUE, TRIM(ITEM.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM) as SAP_MATERIAL_NUM FROM ITEM WHERE DIVISION_GROUP='slsp' AND ITEM_TYPE_CODE = 'SEL' AND TRIM(ITEM.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM) IS NOT NULL GROUP BY TRIM(ITEM.SAP_GRID_VALUE), TRIM(ITEM.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on SAP_ITEM based on the input Style, color, Size, Attribut_cd and get the Material_num and Grid_value. Material_status_code, output either one row.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SAP_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(MATERIAL_NUM) AS MATERIAL_NUM, GRID_VALUE AS GRID_VALUE, LEGACY_STYLE AS LEGACY_STYLE,LEGACY_COLOR AS LEGACY_COLOR, LEGACY_SIZE_CODE_SCALE AS LEGACY_SIZE_CODE_SCALE, LEGACY_ATTRIBUTE AS LEGACY_ATTRIBUTE FROM (SELECT MATERIAL_NUM, GRID_VALUE, LEGACY_STYLE, LEGACY_COLOR, LEGACY_SIZE_CODE_SCALE, LEGACY_ATTRIBUTE, RANK() OVER(PARTITION BY LEGACY_STYLE, LEGACY_COLOR, LEGACY_SIZE_CODE_SCALE, LEGACY_ATTRIBUTE ORDER BY CASE WHEN MATERIAL_STATUS_CODE = '50' THEN 1 WHEN MATERIAL_STATUS_CODE > '50' AND MATERIAL_STATUS_CODE < '99' THEN 2 WHEN MATERIAL_STATUS_CODE > '0' AND MATERIAL_STATUS_CODE < '50' THEN 3 ELSE 4 END , CASE WHEN LEGACY_PUTUP_CODE = '000' THEN 1 ELSE 2 END , MATERIAL_NUM ) RNK FROM SAP_ITEM ) WHERE RNK=1 GROUP BY GRID_VALUE, LEGACY_STYLE, LEGACY_COLOR, LEGACY_SIZE_CODE_SCALE, LEGACY_ATTRIBUTE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: LEGACY_STYLE = I_STYLE AND LEGACY_COLOR = I_COLOR AND LEGACY_ATTRIBUTE = I_ATTRIBUTE_CD AND LEGACY_SIZE_CODE_SCALE = I_SIZE_CD

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, DIVISION_GROUP as DIVISION_GROUP, NVL(STYLE_NUM, '1' ) as STYLE_NUM, NVL(COLOR_CODE, '1' ) as COLOR_CODE, NVL(SIZE_CODE, '1' ) as SIZE_CODE, NVL(ATTRIBUTION_CODE, '1' ) as ATTRIBUTION_CODE, NVL(CUP_SIZE, '1' ) as CUP_SIZE, NVL(SKU, '1' ) as SKU, NVL(DIVISION_CODE, '1' ) as DIVISION_CODE, NVL(COMPANY_CODE, '1' ) as COMPANY_CODE, NVL(SAP_MATERIAL_NUM, '1' ) as SAP_MATERIAL_NUM, NVL(SAP_GRID_VALUE, '1' ) as SAP_GRID_VALUE FROM ( SELECT I.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP) as DIVISION_GROUP, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'slsp',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'slca',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'sli',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'1') as STYLE_NUM, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'slsp',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'slca',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'sli',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'1') as COLOR_CODE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'slsp',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'slca',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'sli',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'1') as SIZE_CODE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slsp',TRIM(I.ATTRIBUTION_CODE),'1') as ATTRIBUTION_CODE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slca',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE),'sli',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE),'1') as CUP_SIZE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slu',TRIM(I.SKU),'sls',TRIM(I.SKU),'sld',TRIM(I.SKU), 'sli', RTRIM(SKU), '1') as SKU, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'sls','1', 'slsp', '1', 'sld', '1', 'slu', '1', TRIM(I.DIVISION_CODE)) as DIVISION_CODE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'sli',TRIM(COMPANY_CODE),'1') as COMPANY_CODE, '1' as SAP_MATERIAL_NUM, '1' as SAP_GRID_VALUE FROM ITEM I WHERE LOWER(TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP)) = LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')) AND I.ITEM_TYPE_CODE = 'SEL' AND I.ITEM_ID IN ( SELECT MIN(I.ITEM_ID) FROM ITEM I WHERE LOWER(TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP)) = LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')) AND I.ITEM_TYPE_CODE = 'SEL' GROUP BY TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP) , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'slsp',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'slca',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'sli',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'slsp',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'slca',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'sli',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'slsp',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'slca',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'sli',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slsp',TRIM(I.ATTRIBUTION_CODE),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slca',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE),'sli',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slu',TRIM(I.SKU),'sls',TRIM(I.SKU),'sld',TRIM(I.SKU), 'sli', RTRIM(SKU), '1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'sls','1', 'slsp', '1', 'sld', '1', 'slu', '1', TRIM(I.DIVISION_CODE)) , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'sli',TRIM(COMPANY_CODE),'1'), '1', '1' ) UNION ALL SELECT I.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP) as DIVISION_GROUP, '1' as STYLE_NUM, '1' as COLOR_CODE, '1' as SIZE_CODE, '1' as ATTRIBUTION_CODE, '1' as CUP_SIZE, '1' as SKU, '1' as DIVISION_CODE, '1' as COMPANY_CODE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slsp',SAP_MATERIAL_NUM, '1' ) as SAP_MATERIAL_NUM, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slsp',SAP_GRID_VALUE, '1' ) as SAP_GRID_VALUE FROM ITEM I WHERE LOWER(TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP)) = LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')) AND LOWER(TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP)) = 'slsp' AND SAP_MATERIAL_NUM IS NOT NULL AND SAP_GRID_VALUE IS NOT NULL AND I.ITEM_TYPE_CODE = 'SEL' AND I.ITEM_ID IN ( SELECT MIN(I.ITEM_ID) FROM ITEM I WHERE LOWER(TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP)) = LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')) AND LOWER(TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP)) = 'slsp' AND I.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM IS NOT NULL AND I.SAP_GRID_VALUE IS NOT NULL AND I.ITEM_TYPE_CODE = 'SEL' GROUP BY I.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM, I.SAP_GRID_VALUE) UNION ALL SELECT I.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP) as DIVISION_GROUP, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'slsp',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'slca',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'sli',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'1') as STYLE_NUM, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'slsp',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'slca',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'sli',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'1') as COLOR_CODE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'slsp',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'slca',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'sli',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'1') as SIZE_CODE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slsp',TRIM(I.ATTRIBUTION_CODE),'1') as ATTRIBUTION_CODE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slca',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE),'sli',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE),'1') as CUP_SIZE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slu',TRIM(I.SKU),'sls',TRIM(I.SKU),'sld',TRIM(I.SKU), 'sli', RTRIM(SKU), '1') as SKU, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'sls','1', 'slsp', '1', 'sld', '1', 'slu', '1', TRIM(I.DIVISION_CODE)) as DIVISION_CODE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'sli',TRIM(COMPANY_CODE),'1') as COMPANY_CODE, '1' as SAP_MATERIAL_NUM, '1' as SAP_GRID_VALUE FROM ITEM I WHERE LOWER(TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP)) = LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')) AND I.ITEM_TYPE_CODE = 'MFG' AND I.ITEM_ID IN ( SELECT MIN(I.ITEM_ID) FROM ITEM I WHERE LOWER(TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP)) = LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')) AND I.ITEM_TYPE_CODE = 'MFG' AND LOWER(TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP)) = 'sli' GROUP BY TRIM(I.DIVISION_GROUP) , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'slsp',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'slca',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'sli',TRIM(I.STYLE_NUM),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'slsp',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'slca',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'sli',TRIM(I.COLOR_CODE),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'slsp',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'slca',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'sli',TRIM(I.SIZE_CODE),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slsp',TRIM(I.ATTRIBUTION_CODE),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slca',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE),'sli',TRIM(I.CUP_SIZE),'1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slu',TRIM(I.SKU),'sls',TRIM(I.SKU),'sld',TRIM(I.SKU), 'sli', RTRIM(SKU), '1') , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'sls','1', 'slsp', '1', 'sld', '1', 'slu', '1', TRIM(I.DIVISION_CODE)) , DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'sli',TRIM(COMPANY_CODE),'1'), '1', '1' ) ) ORDER BY ITEM_ID ASC --

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: DIVISION_GROUP = I_DIVISION_GROUP AND DIVISION_CODE = I_DIVISION_CODE AND COMPANY_CODE = I_COMPANY_CODE AND STYLE_NUM = I_STYLE_NUM AND COLOR_CODE = I_COLOR_CODE AND SIZE_CODE = I_SIZE_CODE AND ATTRIBUTION_CODE = I_ATTRIBUTION_CODE AND CUP_SIZE = I_CUP_SIZE AND SKU = I_SKU AND SAP_MATERIAL_NUM = I_SAP_MATERIAL_NUM AND SAP_GRID_VALUE = I_SAP_GRID_VALUE

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Source qualifier to get required fields and pulls data for all business lines.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_STG_OW_CORP_PROD_ORDER

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT A.PROD_ORDER_NO, A.PARENT_PROD_ORDER, A.STYLE_CD, A.COLOR_CD, A.ATTRIBUTE_CD, A.SIZE_CD, A.MFG_PLANT, A.NET_ORDER_QTY+A.INTRANSIT_QTY AS NET_ORDER_QTY, A.SELLING_STYLE_CD, A.SELLING_COLOR_CD, A.SELLING_ATTRIBUTE_CD, A.SELLING_SIZE_CD, 'A' AS FLAG, A.CURR_DUE_DATE, A.ORIG_DUE_DATE, A.CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT, case when trim(ORDER_SOURCE_CD) in ('ISS') OR a.create_userid = 'StgETLIssProdOrder' then 'W' else case when trim(ORDER_SOURCE_CD) in ( 'XWIP', 'AVYX') then 'P' else 'X'end end as wip_ind , A.SCRAP_QTY FROM STG_OW_CORP_PROD_ORDER A
WHERE CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT IN ($$DIVISION_CODES) AND ORDER_SOURCE_CD NOT IN ('MITS', 'SAP','RWRK') AND ORDER_STATUS_CD = '1' AND AS_OF_DATE = ( SELECT AS_OF_DATE FROM DAY_DIMENSION WHERE DAY_DATE = TRUNC(SYSDATE) -1 ) AND PARENT_PROD_ORDER IS NULL AND SUBSTR(A.PROD_ORDER_NO,1,2) NOT IN ('CT')
UNION ALL
SELECT A.PROD_ORDER_NO, A.PARENT_PROD_ORDER, A.STYLE_CD, A.COLOR_CD, A.ATTRIBUTE_CD, A.SIZE_CD, A.MFG_PLANT, A.NET_ORDER_QTY+A.INTRANSIT_QTY AS NET_ORDER_QTY, A.SELLING_STYLE_CD, A.SELLING_COLOR_CD, A.SELLING_ATTRIBUTE_CD, A.SELLING_SIZE_CD, 'B' AS FLAG, A.CURR_DUE_DATE, A.ORIG_DUE_DATE, A.CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT, case when trim(ORDER_SOURCE_CD) in ('ISS') OR a.create_userid = 'StgETLIssProdOrder' then 'W' else case when trim(ORDER_SOURCE_CD) in ( 'XWIP', 'AVYX') then 'P' else 'X'end end as wip_ind, A.SCRAP_QTY FROM staging.STG_OW_CORP_PROD_ORDER A
WHERE CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT IN ($$DIVISION_CODES) AND ORDER_SOURCE_CD NOT IN ('MITS', 'SAP','RWRK') AND ORDER_STATUS_CD = '1' AND AS_OF_DATE = ( SELECT AS_OF_DATE FROM DAY_DIMENSION WHERE DAY_DATE = TRUNC(SYSDATE) -1 ) AND SUBSTR(A.PROD_ORDER_NO,1,2) NOT IN ('CT')

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on WIP_INV_STATUS to get required fields.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_WIP_INV_STATUS

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT WIP_INV_STATUS.INVENTORY_GRP_CD as INVENTORY_GRP_CD, LPAD((WIP_INV_STATUS.INVENTORY_STAT ),2,0) as INVENTORY_STAT FROM
( select INVENTORY_GRP_CD , INVENTORY_STAT from(
select INVENTORY_GRP_CD , INVENTORY_STAT from (select cast(A.INVENTORY_STAT as int) AS INVENTORY_STAT,a.INVENTORY_GRP_CD from wip_inv_status a join wip_inv_grp b on a.INVENTORY_GRP_CD = b.INVENTORY_GRP_CD join wip_inv_grp c on b.INV_PARENT_GRP_CD = c.INVENTORY_GRP_CD where c.inv_parent_grp_cd in ( '200') and b.inv_parent_grp_cd in ( '210') and trim(TRANSLATE(a.INVENTORY_STAT,'+-.0123456789',' ')) is null) where inventory_stat <= 4
UNION ALL
select INVENTORY_GRP_CD , INVENTORY_STAT from (select cast(A.INVENTORY_STAT as int) AS INVENTORY_STAT,a.INVENTORY_GRP_CD from wip_inv_status a join wip_inv_grp b on a.INVENTORY_GRP_CD = b.INVENTORY_GRP_CD join wip_inv_grp c on b.INV_PARENT_GRP_CD = c.INVENTORY_GRP_CD where c.inv_parent_grp_cd in ( '200') and b.inv_parent_grp_cd in ( '220') and trim(TRANSLATE(a.INVENTORY_STAT,'+-.0123456789',' ')) is null) WHERE inventory_stat > 4 and inventory_stat <= 40
UNION aLL
select INVENTORY_GRP_CD , INVENTORY_STAT from (select cast(A.INVENTORY_STAT as int) AS INVENTORY_STAT,a.INVENTORY_GRP_CD from wip_inv_status a join wip_inv_grp b on a.INVENTORY_GRP_CD = b.INVENTORY_GRP_CD join wip_inv_grp c on b.INV_PARENT_GRP_CD = c.INVENTORY_GRP_CD where c.inv_parent_grp_cd in ( '200') and b.inv_parent_grp_cd in ( '240') and trim(TRANSLATE(a.INVENTORY_STAT,'+-.0123456789',' ')) is null) where inventory_stat > 40 ))WIP_INV_STATUS

ATTRIBUTE.VALUE: DELETE FROM BIWIP_INVENTORY WHERE DIVISION_CODE='UW' AND AS_OF_DATE=(SELECT as_of_date from day_dimension where day_date = trunc(sysdate-1)) and update_userid='ETLTSRSCBIWIP'

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
/*UW*/ SELECT A.PROD_ORDER_NO, A.PARENT_PROD_ORDER, A.STYLE_CD, A.COLOR_CD, A.ATTRIBUTE_CD, A.SIZE_CD, A.MFG_PLANT, A.NET_ORDER_QTY+A.INTRANSIT_QTY AS NET_ORDER_QTY, B.SELLING_STYLE_CD, B.SELLING_COLOR_CD, B.SELLING_ATTRIBUTE_CD, B.SELLING_SIZE_CD, 'A' AS FLAG, A.CURR_DUE_DATE, A.ORIG_DUE_DATE, A.CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT, 'P' AS WIP_IND, A.SCRAP_QTY FROM STG_OW_CORP_PROD_ORDER A JOIN STG_OW_CORP_PROD_ORDER B ON A.PARENT_PROD_ORDER=B.PROD_ORDER_NO AND A.AS_OF_DATE=B.AS_OF_DATE WHERE A.CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT='UNW' AND A.ORDER_STATUS_CD='1' AND A.STYLE_MATL_TYPE_CD IN ('00','01','02') AND A.AS_OF_DATE= ( select as_of_date from day_dimension where day_date = trunc(sysdate-1) ) AND A.PARENT_PROD_ORDER IS NOT NULL AND A.PROD_ORDER_NO NOT LIKE 'CT%'
UNION ALL
SELECT A.PROD_ORDER_NO, A.PARENT_PROD_ORDER, A.STYLE_CD, A.COLOR_CD, A.ATTRIBUTE_CD, A.SIZE_CD, A.MFG_PLANT, A.NET_ORDER_QTY+A.INTRANSIT_QTY AS NET_ORDER_QTY, A.SELLING_STYLE_CD, A.SELLING_COLOR_CD, A.SELLING_ATTRIBUTE_CD, A.SELLING_SIZE_CD, 'B' AS FLAG, A.CURR_DUE_DATE, A.ORIG_DUE_DATE, A.CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT, case when b.parent_prod_order is not null then 'P' when b.PARENT_PROD_ORDER is null and create_userid = 'StgETLIssProdOrder' then 'W' else 'U' end as wip_ind, A.SCRAP_QTY FROM STG_OW_CORP_PROD_ORDER A
left outer join
( select distinct case when instr(PARENT_PROD_ORDER,'-',1,1)<>0 then substr(PARENT_PROD_ORDER,1,instr(PARENT_PROD_ORDER,'-',1,1)-1)
else PARENT_PROD_ORDER end as PARENT_PROD_ORDER from STG_OW_CORP_PROD_ORDER where
as_of_date =( select as_of_date from day_dimension where day_date = trunc(sysdate-1) )
and PARENT_PROD_ORDER is not null AND PROD_ORDER_NO NOT LIKE 'CT%' ) b
on
case when instr(A.prod_order_no,'-',1,1)<>0 then substr(A.prod_order_no,1,instr(A.prod_order_no,'-',1,1)-1) else A.prod_order_no end = b.PARENT_PROD_ORDER
WHERE A.CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT='UNW' AND A.ORDER_STATUS_CD='1' AND A.STYLE_MATL_TYPE_CD IN ('00','01','02') AND A.AS_OF_DATE= ( select as_of_date from day_dimension where day_date = trunc(sysdate-1) ) AND A.PARENT_PROD_ORDER IS NULL AND A.PROD_ORDER_NO NOT LIKE 'CT%' AND A.PROD_ORDER_NO NOT IN ( select distinct PARENT_PROD_ORDER from STG_OW_CORP_PROD_ORDER where as_of_date =( select as_of_date from day_dimension where day_date = trunc(sysdate-1) ) and PARENT_PROD_ORDER is not null AND PROD_ORDER_NO NOT LIKE 'CT%')
UNION ALL
SELECT A.PROD_ORDER_NO, A.PARENT_PROD_ORDER, A.STYLE_CD, A.COLOR_CD, A.ATTRIBUTE_CD, A.SIZE_CD, A.MFG_PLANT, A.NET_ORDER_QTY+A.INTRANSIT_QTY AS NET_ORDER_QTY, A.SELLING_STYLE_CD, A.SELLING_COLOR_CD, A.SELLING_ATTRIBUTE_CD, A.SELLING_SIZE_CD, 'C' AS FLAG, A.CURR_DUE_DATE, A.ORIG_DUE_DATE, A.CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT, 'P' AS WIP_IND, A.SCRAP_QTY FROM
STG_OW_CORP_PROD_ORDER A
WHERE A.CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT='UNW' AND A.ORDER_STATUS_CD='1' AND A.STYLE_MATL_TYPE_CD IN ('00','01','02') AND A.AS_OF_DATE= ( select as_of_date from day_dimension where day_date = trunc(sysdate-1) ) AND A.PROD_ORDER_NO IN ( select distinct PARENT_PROD_ORDER from STG_OW_CORP_PROD_ORDER where as_of_date =( select as_of_date from day_dimension where day_date = trunc(sysdate-1) ) and PARENT_PROD_ORDER is not null AND PROD_ORDER_NO NOT LIKE 'CT%' )
